{"tid":701972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★工作問題不堪壓力 天水圍25歲青年墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-06-14T13:50:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T09:44:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd368f7af34bb2d35b0b81ccf44225e07fbcfee","tid":701972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"凌晨1時許，天水圍發生墮樓案。一名男子被發現倒臥在天瑞邨瑞泉樓對開，嚇煞街坊。保安員見狀立即報案，惟救護員到場時，證實事主已當場斃命，毋須送院搶救。警方介入調查，初步得知事主疑從中層位置墮下，但由於其面容嚴重損毀，暫未能辨識其身份。<br />\n<br />\n警方於凌晨近3時，找到相信屬於死者的住所，原來在隔鄰的瑞心樓。據悉單位內無人應門，於是急召消防到場協助破門入屋進行調查。經初步了解，死者姓梁(25歲)，疑因金錢問題及<span style=\"color: red;\">工作問題不堪壓力</span>，初步相信事件無可疑，列作「屍體發現」案跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/198618/%E7%96%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B0%E6%B7%BB%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D25%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F198618%2F%25E7%2596%2591%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%258F%258A%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%25B7%25BB%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B-%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%259C%258D25%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=edc85695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/198618/%E7%96%91%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A%E8%B2%A1%E5%9B%B0%E6%B7%BB%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D25%E6%AD%B2%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1</a>"},{"pid":"8cad56c46dc19f9b88224966fcf6b34e87f01e7f","tid":701972,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"工作問題不堪壓力<br />\n工作問題不堪壓力<br />\n工作問題不堪壓力"},{"pid":"bda6e538dee13fe97dd19fa096df86edf147a738","tid":701972,"uid":158960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"香港問題 解決唔到"},{"pid":"0b1c34c88d2b10